i>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t6 ore / luna\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tflyere , brosuri , cataloage, sample produse\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t30%\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t2 persoane\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tgratuit 2 persoane\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"#\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tAlege Pachet\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>", "meta_desc": null, "date": "2022-06-08 23:02:33"},{"id": 8992, "title": "Plata", "slug": "plata", "parent_id": 0, "parent_slug": null, "type": "page", "content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>[woocommerce_checkout]</p>\\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->", "meta_desc": null, "date": "2023-04-12 15:01:11"},{"id": 9996, "title": "Homepage", "slug": "homepage", "parent_id": 0, "parent_slug": null, "type": "page", "content": "<h1>NOBLESSE PALACE</h1>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<p>Special Moments That Live Forever!</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>NOBLESSE PALACE<br>OUR STORY</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is a space dedicated to elegance, imposing and fascinating in every architectural detail that is found in its halls. It is a historic building that has been gracefully telling its story for over 140 years. It is a palace located in the heart of Bucharest, an oasis of tranquility set amidst a bohemian garden.<br />Noblesse Palace is a historic building dating from 1881 with a multifunctional role, which has been completely restored, consolidated and refurbished, thus being restored to the cultural and architectural heritage of Bucharest.<br />The Noblesse Palace has been transformed into an arts and events centre, successfully hosting dozens of private events, corporate events, art exhibitions, fashion shows, product launches and more.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Palatul-Noblesse-3-qkthcn81aajjqjmxd1wjepuomfebt71rltt98ymuyg.jpg\\" title=\\"Palatul Noblesse\\" alt=\\"Palatul Noblesse\\" loading=\\"lazy\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"2048\\" height=\\"1365\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-locatie-evenimente-Bucuresti.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-locatie-evenimente-Bucuresti.jpg 2048w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-locatie-evenimente-Bucuresti-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-locatie-evenimente-Bucuresti-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-locatie-evenimente-Bucuresti-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-locatie-evenimente-Bucuresti-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"2048\\" height=\\"1365\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Bucuresti.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Bucuresti.jpg 2048w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Bucuresti-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Bucuresti-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Bucuresti-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Bucuresti-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>NOBLESSE PALACE – OUR SERVICES</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p> Noblesse Palace is a premium event venue, designed to bring people together in an oasis of luxury and elegance.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h4>Fairytale Christening</h4>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"800\\" height=\\"533\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Petrecerea-de-botez-1-1024x682.jpeg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Petrecerea-de-botez-1-1024x682.jpeg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Petrecerea-de-botez-1-600x400.jpeg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Petrecerea-de-botez-1-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Petrecerea-de-botez-1-1536x1023.jpeg 1536w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Petrecerea-de-botez-1.jpeg 1600w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Christening at the Palace is undoubtedly one of those private events brimming with pure emotion, love, and the promise of a new beginning. For the celebration of this special event, Noblesse Palace transforms into that fairytale place with princes and princesses, where the universe creates the perfect setting for this occasion.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/fairytale-christening/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tDiscover More\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h4>Dream Wedding</h4>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"800\\" height=\\"534\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sedinta-foto-de-nunta-1024x683.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sedinta-foto-de-nunta-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sedinta-foto-de-nunta-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sedinta-foto-de-nunta-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sedinta-foto-de-nunta-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sedinta-foto-de-nunta.jpg 2048w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>A wedding at the Palace is and will remain every woman’s dream. We strongly believe that every woman has imagined, at least once in her lifetime, being a princess from childhood fairy tales on her wedding day. Located in the heart of Bucharest, Noblesse Palace fulfills this desire, making it unique and elevating it to the standard dreamed of by a princess.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/dream-wedding/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tDiscover More\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h4>Corporate Events</h4>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"800\\" height=\\"534\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Art-Lunch-la-Palatul-Noblesse-3-1-1024x683.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Art-Lunch-la-Palatul-Noblesse-3-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Art-Lunch-la-Palatul-Noblesse-3-1-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Art-Lunch-la-Palatul-Noblesse-3-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Art-Lunch-la-Palatul-Noblesse-3-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Art-Lunch-la-Palatul-Noblesse-3-1.jpg 2048w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is an event venue located in the center of Bucharest, near University Square, just 5 minutes away from Universitate metro station. This premium event venue is a symbol of elegance and luxury, capable of hosting a wide range of corporate events. Noblesse Palace is surrounded by a beautiful Parisian garden suitable for outdoor corporate events.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/services/corporate-events/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tDiscover More\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>noblesse palace overview</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tSix rooms with different styles, comprising the ground floor of Noblesse Palace (Gallery, Luxury, Regent, Florence, Baroque and Opera)\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tBiblioteka is a unique space located in the basement with direct access to the garden. Here you can organize small  events\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tThe bohemian garden, a generous courtyard of 600 square meters, an oasis of greenery and intimacy in the historic atmosphere of Bucharest\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tMaximum capacity indoors is 140 people (seated) and 300 people (cocktail style)\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tNearby parking spaces, available upon request\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tThe Noblesse Palace is equipped with state-of-the-art technological facilities\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>why choose the noblesse palace?</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>19th century historical building</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is a historical building from the 19th century, is the first building with an eclectic architecture built in this old area of Bucharest, and bears the signature of the famous romanian architect Alexandru Săvulescu.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Fully consolidated and restored building</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is the only completely consolidated and restored palace to the highest standards in Bucharest, where luxurious architecture merges with its intimate elegance.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Central Premium Venue</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is a premium venue located in the center of Bucharest, near Universitate Square, just 5 minutes away from Universitate metro station.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>unique experience</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace offers a unique and comprehensive experience. Rediscover 135 years of history brought to life by the architects and designers of Noblesse Group.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Exclusive tours of the palace</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>You can enjoy exclusive tours of Noblesse Palace. During this tours you can have the opportunity to visit Fusion Arts exhibitions, as well as the latest international interior design collections in the <a href=\\"https://noblesse-group.com/\\">Noblesse Group</a> portfolio.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>We have experience in organizing hundreds of events</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>With experience in hundreds of successful events organized for major companies across all industries, as well as private clients, Noblesse Palace has hosted weddings, baptisms, birthdays parties, conferences, workshops, product launches, and much more.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>The Church of Holy Saints</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>The Church of the Holy Saints (Biserica Sfinților) in Bucharest is located near Noblesse Palace. The church is famous for its murals, which have been well-preserved over time. Welcoming and warm, it has witnessed many beautiful stories organized at Noblesse Palace, with many couples and parents choosing this church for religious ceremonies.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Victorian Apartament</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>For moments of rest and comfort for the newlyweds or parents, Noblesse Palace provides an apartment on the upper floor, the Princess Room, fully functional and equipped to the highest standards, ensuring that the evening spent at the Palace is truly memorable</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/146-1.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"1e35e1f\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"146 (1)\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTA3NjIsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wM1wvMTQ2LTEuanBnIiwic2xpZGVzaG93IjoiMWUzNWUxZiJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-253.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"1e35e1f\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Nobless shooting - 253\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTA0MzUsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wM1wvTm9ibGVzcy1zaG9vdGluZy0yNTMuanBnIiwic2xpZGVzaG93IjoiMWUzNWUxZiJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-040.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"1e35e1f\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Nobless shooting - 040\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTA0MzAsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wM1wvTm9ibGVzcy1zaG9vdGluZy0wNDAuanBnIiwic2xpZGVzaG93IjoiMWUzNWUxZiJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Botez-Valeria-By-Ioana-Porav-Fine-Art-Photographer.10.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"1e35e1f\\" data-eleme