settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTA3OTgsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wM1wvTm9ibGVzcy1zaG9vdGluZy0yMzYuanBnIiwic2xpZGVzaG93IjoiMWUzNWUxZiJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Evenimante-Private-la-Palatul-Noblesse.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"1e35e1f\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Evenimante Private la Palatul Noblesse\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTA4MjQsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wM1wvRXZlbmltYW50ZS1Qcml2YXRlLWxhLVBhbGF0dWwtTm9ibGVzc2UuanBnIiwic2xpZGVzaG93IjoiMWUzNWUxZiJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Preview-105.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"1e35e1f\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Preview-105\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTA0MzksInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wM1wvUHJldmlldy0xMDUuanBnIiwic2xpZGVzaG93IjoiMWUzNWUxZiJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\thttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=35SQiMsvHMA&#038;ab_channel=NoblesseGroup\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>NOBLESSE PALACE - events and art centre in Bucharest</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>The Noblesse Palace is a premium central location for private events, corporate events, art events, networking events and more.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h2 data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tPalatul Noblesse\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h2>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tBiblioteka\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"1365\\" height=\\"2048\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Biblioteka.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Biblioteka.jpg 1365w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Biblioteka-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Biblioteka-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Biblioteka-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Biblioteka-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 1365px) 100vw, 1365px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Biblioteka Hub is an urban, industrial design concept, a space dedicated to courses, conferences, workshops, trainings, brainstorming meetings and, last but not least, private events, especially aniversary and birthday parties. Biblioteka Hubconsists of two rooms, a main room and a secondary room that serves as a space for coffee breaks and socialising.<br />The logistical support provided is of the highest quality, the room is equipped with a video projector, laptop, fan convectors with hot and cold air thermostats, WI-FI internet and a high-performance sound system.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/biblioteka\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tBiblioteka Hub\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h2 data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tPalatul Noblesse\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h2>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tGround Floor\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"1365\\" height=\\"2048\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Paltul-Noblesse-Locatie-evenimente-Bucuresti.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Paltul-Noblesse-Locatie-evenimente-Bucuresti.jpg 1365w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Paltul-Noblesse-Locatie-evenimente-Bucuresti-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Paltul-Noblesse-Locatie-evenimente-Bucuresti-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Paltul-Noblesse-Locatie-evenimente-Bucuresti-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Paltul-Noblesse-Locatie-evenimente-Bucuresti-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 1365px) 100vw, 1365px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>The ground floor of the Noblesse Palace is a space that speaks of elegance and refinement, a space for private events and corporate events that turn into memorable events. The ground floor of the Palais Noblesse is a compartmentalised space, represented by five rooms, each room presenting a different architectural style, from the Baroque style found in the central hall, to the Florentine, Louis XV and XVI styles and even the classical or contemporary style.<br />The rooms are equipped with sound system, mixer, microphone, WiFi internet, video projector, screen, air conditioning and more.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/ground-floor/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tGround Floor\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h2 data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tpalatul noblesse\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h2>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tThe Garden\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"1363\\" height=\\"2048\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gala-Kudika-la-Palatul-Noblesse-07.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gala-Kudika-la-Palatul-Noblesse-07.jpg 1363w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gala-Kudika-la-Palatul-Noblesse-07-399x600.jpg 399w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gala-Kudika-la-Palatul-Noblesse-07-682x1024.jpg 682w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gala-Kudika-la-Palatul-Noblesse-07-768x1154.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gala-Kudika-la-Palatul-Noblesse-07-1022x1536.jpg 1022w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 1363px) 100vw, 1363px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>The garden of the Palais Noblesse is a bohemian, Parisian garden, an oasis of calm surrounded by vibrant colours. Surrounding the palace with its understated elegance, the garden covers an area of 600 square metres and is an irresistible attraction for those looking for a central location for outdoor events. With its romantic atmosphere and idyllic scenery, the garden is the ideal venue for special events like private events and corporate events. From weddings and christenings to private parties and corporate events, this natural setting adds a touch of elegance and sophistication to any occasion.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/the-garden/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tThe Garden\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Discover the Noblesse Palace</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is a space dedicated to classical elegance, imposing and fascinating in every architectural detail, which can be found in its halls.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/discover-the-palace/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tNoblesse Palace\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h4>Noblesse Palace <br/>\\nEvent & Art Center in bucharest</h4>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Step into our Universe and explore each room. Discover a place full of history and history.</p><p>As an events and art center, Noblesse Palace stands as a true architectural and cultural gem in the heart of Bucharest.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"/turvirtual/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tVirtual Tour\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/eveniment/eveniment-aniversar-centrul-filia/\\" title=\\"Centrul Filia &#8211; eveniment aniversar organizat la Palatul Noblesse, aprilie 2024\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Eveniment-aniversar-Centru-Filia-la-Palatul-Noblesse-2-500x500.jpeg\\" alt=\\"Centrul Filia &#8211; eveniment aniversar organizat la Palatul Noblesse, aprilie 2024\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"javascript:void(0);\\" title=\\"Start Date:22 aprilie @ 6:00 pm  - End Date:22 aprilie @ 10:30 pm\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t22\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tapr.\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/eveniment/eveniment-aniversar-centrul-filia/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\tCentrul Filia &#8211; eveniment aniversar organizat la Palatul Noblesse, aprilie 2024\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\tCentrul FILIA sărbătorește 24 de ani de activitate și dăruire în construirea unei lumi mai&hellip;\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/eveniment/lansarea-grupului-bni-scale-up/\\" title=\\"Lansarea oficială a Grupului BNI Scale Up a fost un succes total!\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/BNI-Scale-Up-la-Palatul-Noblesse-500x500.jpeg\\" alt=\\"Lansarea oficială a Grupului BNI Scale Up a fost un succes total!\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"javascript:void(0);\\" title=\\"Start Date:19 aprilie @ 6:30 pm  - End Date:19 aprilie @ 10:30 pm\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t19\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tapr.\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/eveniment/lansarea-grupului-bni-scale-up/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\tLansarea oficială a Grupului BNI Scale Up a fost un succes total!\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\tBNI Scale Up, primul grup BNI care își organizează întâlnirile seara, a avut o lansare&hellip;\\t\\t\\n\\t\