lementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"6a23d10\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"IMG_20230328_094352\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6OTU0OCwidXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6XC9cL3d3dy5wYWxhdHVsbm9ibGVzc2Uucm9cL3dwLWNvbnRlbnRcL3VwbG9hZHNcLzIwMjNcLzA4XC9JTUdfMjAyMzAzMjhfMDk0MzUyLTEuanBnIiwic2xpZGVzaG93IjoiNmEyM2QxMCJ9\\">\\n</a>\\n<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/IMG_20230321_101302-1.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"6a23d10\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"IMG_20230321_101302\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6OTU4MCwidXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6XC9cL3d3dy5wYWxhdHVsbm9ibGVzc2Uucm9cL3dwLWNvbnRlbnRcL3VwbG9hZHNcLzIwMjNcLzA4XC9JTUdfMjAyMzAzMjFfMTAxMzAyLTEuanBnIiwic2xpZGVzaG93IjoiNmEyM2QxMCJ9\\">\\n</a>\\n<iframe loading=\\"lazy\\"\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tsrc=\\"https://maps.google.com/maps?q=Palatul%20Noblesse%2C%20bucuresti&#038;t=m&#038;z=15&#038;output=embed&#038;iwloc=near\\"\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\ttitle=\\"Palatul Noblesse, bucuresti\\"\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\taria-label=\\"Palatul Noblesse, bucuresti\\"\\n\\t\\t\\t></iframe>", "meta_desc": null, "date": "2023-08-15 20:09:38"},{"id": 9455, "title": "Fusion Arts Fair - Fall Into Art", "slug": "fusion-arts-fair-fall-into-art", "parent_id": 5730, "parent_slug": "evenimente-proprii", "type": "page", "content": "<h1>Fusion Arts Fair</h1>Fall Into Art<h1>Fusion Arts Fair</h1>Fall Into Art\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tPrevious slide\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tNext slide\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>FUSION ARTS FAIR - FALL INTO ART</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\tExpoziție de artă cu vânzare\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t Days Hours Minutes Seconds\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\tPentru  a participa la această expoziție, te rugăm să completezi formularul de înregistrare\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.facebook.com/palatulnoblesse\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noopener\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tFacebook\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.instagram.com/palatulnoblesse/\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noopener\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tInstagram\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.youtube.com/@noblessegroup147/videos\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noopener\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tYoutube\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>", "meta_desc": "Fusion Ars Fair – Fall Into Art își propune să atragă atenția asupra diversității și profunzimii creației artistice contemporane românești. ", "date": "2023-08-24 11:13:04"},{"id": 11085, "title": "Services", "slug": "services", "parent_id": 0, "parent_slug": null, "type": "page", "content": "<p>Special Moments That Live Forever!</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>SERVICES<br>PALATUL NOBLESSE</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace, a former 19th-century boyar residence located in the center of Bucharest, has been completely restored and brought back to life. Today, it stands as one of the most important centers for culture, art, and design, boasting a unique concept in Europe. This premium event venue was created to bring people together in an oasis of luxury and elegance.<br />Through its team of event organizers, Noblesse Palace offers a comprehensive range of services for both private and corporate events.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>NOBLESSE PALACE – EVENT PLANNING SERVICES</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h2 data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tPalatul Noblesse\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h2>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tCorporate Events\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"1365\\" height=\\"2048\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Servicii-Evenimente-Corporate.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Servicii-Evenimente-Corporate.jpg 1365w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Servicii-Evenimente-Corporate-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Servicii-Evenimente-Corporate-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Servicii-Evenimente-Corporate-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Servicii-Evenimente-Corporate-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 1365px) 100vw, 1365px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Palatul Noblesse is an event venue located in the centre of Bucharest, in the University Square area, just 5 minutes from Universitate metro station. This premium event venue can host a variety of corporate events.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/services/corporate-events/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tDiscover Moree\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h2 data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tPalatul Noblesse\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h2>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tPrivate Events\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"1365\\" height=\\"2048\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Servicii-Evenimente-Private.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Servicii-Evenimente-Private.jpg 1365w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Servicii-Evenimente-Private-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Servicii-Evenimente-Private-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Servicii-Evenimente-Private-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Servicii-Evenimente-Private-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 1365px) 100vw, 1365px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Since its opening, Noblesse Palace has hosted numerous private events (weddings, christenings, private parties, photo shoots), each one writing a page of history for the most beautiful and unforgettable moments of our guests' lives.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/private-events/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tDiscover More\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h2 data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tpalatul noblesse\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h2>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tBrand Events\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"1365\\" height=\\"2048\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Fusion-Arts-1.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Fusion-Arts-1.jpg 1365w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Fusion-Arts-1-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Fusion-Arts-1-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Fusion-Arts-1-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Fusion-Arts-1-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 1365px) 100vw, 1365px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>We've brought back the charm and noble elegance of the 19th century, enabling us to conceptualize, create, and organize some of the most esteemed events in art, culture, and socializing.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/services/our-concepts/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tDiscover More\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>why choose the noblesse palace?</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tSix rooms with different styles, comprising the ground floor of Noblesse Palace (Gallery, Luxury, Regent, Florence, Baroque and Opera)\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tBiblioteka is a unique space located in the basement with direct access to the garden. Here you can organize small  events\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tThe bohemian garden, a generous courtyard of 600 square meters, an oasis of greenery and intimacy in the historic atmosphere of Bucharest\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tMaximum capacity indoors is 140 people (seated) and 300 people (cocktail style)\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tNearby parking spaces, available upon request\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tThe Noblesse Palace is equipped with state-of-the-art technological facilities\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>19th century historical building</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is a historical building from the 19th century, is the first building with an eclectic architecture built in this old area of Bucharest, and bears the signature of the famous romanian architect Alexandru Săvulescu.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Fully consolidated and restored building</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is the only completely consolidated and restored palace to the highest standards in Bucharest, where luxurious architecture merges with its intimate elegance.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Central Premium Venue</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is a premium venue located in the center of Bucharest, near Universitate Square, just 5 minutes away from Universitate metro station.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>unique experience</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace offers a unique and comprehensive experience. Rediscover 135 years of history brought to life by the architects and designers of Noblesse Group.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Exclusive tours of the palace</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>You can enjoy exclusive tours of Noblesse Palace. During this tours you can have the opportunity to visit Fusion Arts exhibitions, as well as the latest international interior design collections in the <a href=\\"https://noblesse-group.com/\\">Noblesse Group</a> portfolio.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>We have experience in organizing hundreds of events</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>With experience in hundreds of successful events organized for major companies across all industries, as well as private clients, Noblesse Palace has hosted weddings, baptisms, birthdays parties, conferences, workshops, product launches, and much more.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>The Church of Holy Saints</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>The Church of the Holy Saints (Biserica Sfinților) in Bucharest is located near Noblesse Palace. The church is famous for its murals, which have been well-preserved over time. Welcoming and warm, it has witnessed many beautiful stories organized at Noblesse Palace, with many couples and parents choosing this church for religious ceremonies.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Victorian Apartament</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>For moments of rest and comfort for the newlyweds or parents, Noblesse Palace provides an apartment on the upper floor, the Princess Room, fully functional and equipped to the highest standards, ensuring that the evening spent at the Palace is truly memorable</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Servicii-Palatul-Noblesse-2.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"696c5461\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Botez Valeria\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTA3NjgsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wM1wvU2VydmljaWktUGFsYXR1bC