\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/detalii-32.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"696c5461\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"detalii-32\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTA3OTAsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wM1wvZGV0YWxpaS0zMi5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiI2OTZjNTQ2MSJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>NOBLESSE PALACE - FULL RANGE OF SERVICES</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>We offer a full range of services for both private and corporate events.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tEvent Planner\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tEvent Design\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tCustomized Menus\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tFloral Arrangements\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tPhoto - Video Services\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tEntertainment \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tPiano Reantal\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h4>PLANNING AN EVENT?</h4>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Please fill out the contact form, and we will get back to you shortly with a personalized price quotation.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/contact/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tContact Form\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>", "meta_desc": "Services - Through its team of event organizers, Noblesse Palace offers a comprehensive range of services for both private and corporate events.", "date": "2024-04-14 09:37:53"},{"id": 11090, "title": "Corporate Events", "slug": "corporate-events", "parent_id": 11085, "parent_slug": "services", "type": "page", "content": "<p>Special Moments That Live Forever!</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>Noblesse Palace – Lifestyle Palace<br>your Host for successful corporate events</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\tNoblesse Palace is an event venue located in the center of Bucharest, near University Square, just 5 minutes away from Universitate metro station. This premium event venue is a symbol of elegance and luxury, capable of hosting a wide range of corporate events.<br>Noblesse Palace is a 19th-century historic building with exceptional architecture and a rich history, distinguished by its royal atmosphere and top-notch services. It is a versatile, impressive space suitable for those who want to stand out and showcase their brand.<br>Surrounded by a bohemian garden in the Parisian style, abundant with color and light, Noblesse Palace creates that enchanting atmosphere where every corporate event transforms into a precious memory.\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>Corporate events - discover the palace</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h2 data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tPalatul Noblesse\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h2>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tBiblioteka\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"1365\\" height=\\"2048\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Biblioteka.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Biblioteka.jpg 1365w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Biblioteka-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Biblioteka-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Biblioteka-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Biblioteka-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 1365px) 100vw, 1365px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Biblioteka Hub is an urban, industrial design concept, a space dedicated to courses, conferences, workshops, trainings, brainstorming meetings and, last but not least, private events, especially aniversary and birthday parties. Biblioteka Hubconsists of two rooms, a main room and a secondary room that serves as a space for coffee breaks and socialising.<br />The logistical support provided is of the highest quality, the room is equipped with a video projector, laptop, fan convectors with hot and cold air thermostats, WI-FI internet and a high-performance sound system.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/biblioteka/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tBiblioteka Hub\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h2 data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tPalatul Noblesse\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h2>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tGround Floor\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"1365\\" height=\\"2048\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Paltul-Noblesse-Locatie-evenimente-Bucuresti.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Paltul-Noblesse-Locatie-evenimente-Bucuresti.jpg 1365w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Paltul-Noblesse-Locatie-evenimente-Bucuresti-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Paltul-Noblesse-Locatie-evenimente-Bucuresti-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Paltul-Noblesse-Locatie-evenimente-Bucuresti-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Paltul-Noblesse-Locatie-evenimente-Bucuresti-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 1365px) 100vw, 1365px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>The ground floor of the Noblesse Palace is a space that speaks of elegance and refinement, a space for private events and corporate events that turn into memorable events. The ground floor of the Palais Noblesse is a compartmentalised space, represented by five rooms, each room presenting a different architectural style, from the Baroque style found in the central hall, to the Florentine, Louis XV and XVI styles and even the classical or contemporary style.<br />The rooms are equipped with sound system, mixer, microphone, WiFi internet, video projector, screen, air conditioning and more.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/ground-floor/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tGround Floor\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h2 data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tpalatul noblesse\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h2>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tThe Garden\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"1363\\" height=\\"2048\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gala-Kudika-la-Palatul-Noblesse-07.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gala-Kudika-la-Palatul-Noblesse-07.jpg 1363w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gala-Kudika-la-Palatul-Noblesse-07-399x600.jpg 399w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gala-Kudika-la-Palatul-Noblesse-07-682x1024.jpg 682w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gala-Kudika-la-Palatul-Noblesse-07-768x1154.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Gala-Kudika-la-Palatul-Noblesse-07-1022x1536.jpg 1022w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 1363px) 100vw, 1363px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>The garden of the Palais Noblesse is a bohemian, Parisian garden, an oasis of calm surrounded by vibrant colours. Surrounding the palace with its understated elegance, the garden covers an area of 600 square metres and is an irresistible attraction for those looking for a central location for outdoor events. With its romantic atmosphere and idyllic scenery, the garden is the ideal venue for special events. From weddings and christenings to private parties and corporate events, this natural setting adds a touch of elegance and sophistication to any occasion.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/the-garden/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tThe Garden\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Evenimente-Corporate-la-Palatul-Noblesse-4.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"79287d62\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Evenimente Corporate la Palatul Noblesse\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTA3MTksInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wM1wvRXZlbmltZW50ZS1Db3Jwb3JhdGUtbGEtUGFsYXR1bC1Ob2JsZXNzZS00LmpwZyIsInNsaWRlc2hvdyI6Ijc5Mjg3ZDYyIn0%3D\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Evenimente-Corporate-la-Palatul-Noblesse-5.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"79287d62\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Evenimente Corporate la Palatul Noblesse\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTA3MzgsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wM1wvRXZlbmltZW50ZS1Db3Jwb3JhdGUtbGEtUGFsYXR1bC1Ob2JsZXNzZS01LmpwZyIsInNsaWRlc2hvdyI6Ijc5Mjg3ZDYyIn0%3D\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Cina-de-gala-10.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"y