t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/DSC_7059.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"79287d62\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"DSC_7059\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTA3OTIsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wM1wvRFNDXzcwNTkuanBnIiwic2xpZGVzaG93IjoiNzkyODdkNjIifQ%3D%3D\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/HRS__1134-HDR.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"79287d62\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"HRS__1134-HDR\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTA3OTYsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wM1wvSFJTX18xMTM0LUhEUi5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiI3OTI4N2Q2MiJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/events/category/corporate-events/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tCorporate Events Portfolio\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>CORPORATE EVENTS - FACILITIES</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>We are offering a wide a range of facilities and services for memorable corporate events. Our event planners will be with you every step of the way, guiding you on the path to the most beautiful event of your life.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tSix rooms with different styles, comprising the ground floor of Noblesse Palace (Gallery, Luxury, Regent, Florence, Baroque and Opera)\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tBiblioteka is a unique space located in the basement with direct access to the garden. Here you can organize small  evevents\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tThe bohemian garden, a generous courtyard of 600 square meters, an oasis of greenery and intimacy in the historic atmosphere of Bucharest\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tMaximum capacity indoors is 140 people (seated) and 300 people (cocktail style)\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tNearby parking spaces, available upon request\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tNoblesse Palace is equipped with modern technical amenities\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>why choose noblesse palace for your corporate events?</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>19th century historical building</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is a historical building from the 19th century, is the first building with an eclectic architecture built in this old area of Bucharest, and bears the signature of the famous romanian architect Alexandru Săvulescu.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Fully consolidated and restored building</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is the only completely consolidated and restored palace to the highest standards in Bucharest, where luxurious architecture merges with its intimate elegance.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Central Premium Venue</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is a premium venue located in the center of Bucharest, near Universitate Square, just 5 minutes away from Universitate metro station.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>unique experience</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace offers a unique and comprehensive experience. Rediscover 135 years of history brought to life by the architects and designers of Noblesse Group.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Exclusive tours of the palace</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>You can enjoy exclusive tours of Noblesse Palace. During this tours you can have the opportunity to visit Fusion Arts exhibitions, as well as the latest international interior design collections in the <a href=\\"https://noblesse-group.com/\\">Noblesse Group</a> portfolio.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>We have experience in organizing hundreds of events</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>With experience in hundreds of successful events organized for major companies across all industries, as well as private clients, Noblesse Palace has hosted weddings, baptisms, birthdays parties, conferences, workshops, product launches, and much more.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>The Church of Holy Saints</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>The Church of the Holy Saints (Biserica Sfinților) in Bucharest is located near Noblesse Palace. The church is famous for its murals, which have been well-preserved over time. Welcoming and warm, it has witnessed many beautiful stories organized at Noblesse Palace, with many couples and parents choosing this church for religious ceremonies.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Victorian Apartament</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>For moments of rest and comfort for the newlyweds or parents, Noblesse Palace provides an apartment on the upper floor, the Princess Room, fully functional and equipped to the highest standards, ensuring that the evening spent at the Palace is truly memorable</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h4>CORPORATE EVENTS – FULL RANGE OF SERVICES\\n</h4>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>We provide high standards facilities and services. We want our Palace to be the place where your corporate events will benefit from that uniqueness and exceed all expectations.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tEvent Manager\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tEvent Design\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tCustomized Menus\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tFloral Arrangements\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tPhoto - Video Services\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tEntertainment \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tPiano Rental\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h4>Planning a corporate event?</h4>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Please fill out the contact form, and we will get back to you shortly with a personalized price quotation.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/contact/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tContact Form\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>", "meta_desc": "This premium event venue is a symbol of elegance and luxury, capable of hosting a wide range of corporate events.", "date": "2024-04-14 10:00:39"},{"id": 11105, "title": "Dream Wedding", "slug": "dream-wedding", "parent_id": 0, "parent_slug": null, "type": "page", "content": "<h2>Special Moments That Live Forever!</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>Noblesse Palace – Lifestyle Palace<br>The fairytale place where every dream turns into reality.</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\tIn the heart of Bucharest lies a special place, a place seemingly torn from fairytales, a place that turns dreams into reality: Noblesse Palace. Here, love stories are written for the newlyweds who want their wedding day to be memorable, both for themselves and their loved ones.<br>A dream wedding at Noblesse Palace is an event taken straight from childhood fairytales, a love story transposed into a unique, royal atmosphere. A dream wedding at Noblesse Palace is an exclusive, elegant, intimate event attended only by family and closest friends.<br>From the very first steps, luxury and refinement make their presence felt. The marble flooring in shades of white and black, as well as the large windows flooding the rooms with natural light, the precious furniture, the spectacular chandeliers, and the contemporary artworks adorning the walls all contribute to creating a fairytale setting, a royal frame that guests at the dream wedding will enjoy throughout the event.<br>A wedding at Noblesse Palace is an intimate and elegant affair. The palace offers the possibility of organizing select and intimate events to create a closer and more personal atmosphere.\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Nobless-shooting-236-ql7fywei2c7pcgpzme6tkp1vx349ajzjc2phr59j08.jpg\\" title=\\"Nobless shooting &#8211; 236\\" alt=\\"Nobless shooting - 236\\" loading=\\"lazy\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"2048\\" height=\\"1365\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-310.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-310.jpg 2048w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-310-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-310-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-310-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-310-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"2048\\" height=\\"1365\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Botez-la-Palatul-Noblesse.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Botez-la-Palatul-Noblesse.jpg 2048w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Botez-la-Palatul-Noblesse-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Botez-la-Palatul-Noblesse-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Botez-la-Palatul-Noblesse-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Botez-la-Palatul-Noblesse-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>WHY CHOOSE NOBLESSE PALACE FOR YOUR DREAM WEDDING?</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>Noblesse Palace - Historical Building</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is the only fully consolidated and restored palace to the highest standards in Bucharest.</p><p>It is a historic building from the 19th century, the first eclectic-style building constructed in the center of Bucharest, bearing the signature of the famous architect Alexandru Săvulescu.</p><p>Noblesse Palace is a centrally located premium venue (situated in the center of Bucharest, just 5 minutes away from University Square).</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"800\\" height=\\"534\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-1024x683.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6.jpg 2048w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"800\\" height=\\"534\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7-1024x683.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7.jpg 2048w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>Noblesse Palace - Ballrooms</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Refinement and luxury are criteria found in all components of the palace.</p><p>The ballrooms of Noblesse Palace are versatile, decorated in various styles, ensuring intimacy and the possibility of organizing memorable, unique events.</p><p>The palace is surrounded by a generous courtyard of 600 square meters, an oasis of greenery and intimacy in the historic atmosphere of Bucharest.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>Customized Services</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Our event planners has the experience of hundreds of events organized, hundreds of memorable events, and thousands of memories created for every couple who has crossed our threshold.</p><p>Our team understands that each couple is unique and has their own desires and visions for their dream wedding. Therefore, the services offered are comprehensive and personalized to meet all the needs and desires of the newlyweds.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"800\\" height=\\"534\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-051-1024x683.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-051-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-051-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-051-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-051-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-051.jpg 2048w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Nunta-de-vis-ql7h16drsk8dvl5fdz212mei3ve02wrky25pw460d4.jpg\\" title=\\"Nunta de vis\\" alt=\\"Nunta de vis\\" loading=\\"lazy\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>Wedding Photo Sessions</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is an ideal setting for wedding photoshoots. Its eclectic architecture, rooms decorated in various styles, and green garden all provide spectacular backdrops for unforgettable photographs.</p><p>Couples can enjoy romantic moments captured in images, transporting them back to this special day every time they look at the photo album.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Aranjamente-Florale-de-nunta.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"4d208abe\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Aranjamente Florale de nunta\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTA4MjksInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wM1wvQXJhbmphbWVudGUtRmxvcmFsZS1kZS1udW50YS5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiI0ZDIwOGFiZSJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-236.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"4d208abe\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Nobless shooting - 236\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTA3OTgsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wM1wvTm9ibGVzcy1zaG9vdGluZy0yMzYuanBnIiwic2xpZGVzaG93IjoiNGQyMDhhYmUifQ%3D%3D\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nunta-de-vis-la-Palatul-Noblesse-2-1.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slide