t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h4>planning a dream Wedding?</h4>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Please fill out the contact form, and we will get back to you shortly with a personalized price quotation.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/contact/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tContact form\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>", "meta_desc": "A dream wedding at Noblesse Palace is an event taken straight from childhood fairytales, a love story transposed into a unique, royal atmosphere. ", "date": "2024-04-14 08:34:33"},{"id": 11115, "title": "FAIRYTALE CHRISTENING", "slug": "fairytale-christening", "parent_id": 0, "parent_slug": null, "type": "page", "content": "<p>Special Moments That Live Forever!</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>A fairytale christening at Noblesse Palace: An intimate celebration in a spectacular setting.</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>In the heart of the city, in a setting filled with history and elegance, Noblesse Palace becomes the stage for a special and sacred event: the christening. For parents who wish to celebrate the joy and blessing brought into their lives through an intimate event, Noblesse Palace offers a spectacular backdrop and comprehensive services for organizing a fairytale christening.</p><p>Noblesse Palace, a historic building erected in 1881, is renowned for its architectural refinement and special design, expertly blending eclectic style with modern and contemporary elements. The enchanting ground-floor halls, each with its distinct architectural style, provide the perfect space for organizing an intimate and personalized christening. The high ceilings and large windows allow natural light to flood the rooms, creating a magical and warm atmosphere. The precious furniture and spectacular chandeliers, along with contemporary artworks adorning the walls, all add a special charm to the event, making the christening truly fairytale-like. The special marble flooring emphasizes the elegance of the venue and lends a regal air to the entire space.</p><p>An intimate christening offers the opportunity for new parents to focus on the closest people in their lives and spend special moments with them. Noblesse Palace is the ideal place for such intimate gatherings, where a warm and welcoming atmosphere can truly be felt.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Preview-105-ql1lox6lthhfqwjcz899vybtaiksw9p4k5t1teambc.jpg\\" title=\\"Preview-105\\" alt=\\"Preview-105\\" loading=\\"lazy\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"1600\\" height=\\"1066\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tendinte-botez-2024.jpeg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tendinte-botez-2024.jpeg 1600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tendinte-botez-2024-600x400.jpeg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tendinte-botez-2024-1024x682.jpeg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tendinte-botez-2024-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Tendinte-botez-2024-1536x1023.jpeg 1536w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"1600\\" height=\\"1066\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Petrecerea-de-botez-1.jpeg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Petrecerea-de-botez-1.jpeg 1600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Petrecerea-de-botez-1-600x400.jpeg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Petrecerea-de-botez-1-1024x682.jpeg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Petrecerea-de-botez-1-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Petrecerea-de-botez-1-1536x1023.jpeg 1536w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>why choose noblesse palace for A fairytale christening</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Noblesse Palace - Historical Building</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is the only fully consolidated and restored palace to the highest standards in Bucharest.</p><p>It is a historic building from the 19th century, the first eclectic-style building constructed in the center of Bucharest, bearing the signature of the famous architect Alexandru Săvulescu.</p><p>Noblesse Palace is a centrally located premium venue (situated in the center of Bucharest, just 5 minutes away from University Square).</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"800\\" height=\\"534\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-1024x683.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6.jpg 2048w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"800\\" height=\\"534\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7-1024x683.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7-768x512.jpg 768w, htt