lesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sedinta-Foto-Profesionala-la-Palatul-Noblesse.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sedinta-Foto-Profesionala-la-Palatul-Noblesse.jpg 2048w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sedinta-Foto-Profesionala-la-Palatul-Noblesse-600x402.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sedinta-Foto-Profesionala-la-Palatul-Noblesse-1024x686.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sedinta-Foto-Profesionala-la-Palatul-Noblesse-768x515.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sedinta-Foto-Profesionala-la-Palatul-Noblesse-1536x1029.jpg 1536w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"2048\\" height=\\"1372\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sedinta-foto.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sedinta-foto.jpg 2048w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sedinta-foto-600x402.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sedinta-foto-1024x686.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sedinta-foto-768x515.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sedinta-foto-1536x1029.jpg 1536w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>photo sessions at noblesse palace</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Wedding Photo Sessions</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace becomes the ideal choice for immortalizing one of the most important days in a couple's life. The historic and imposing building, with its spectacular halls, adds a royal touch to the photo session and contributes to creating storybook photographs. The large windows, precious furniture, and spectacular chandeliers are just a few of the elements that will add an air of elegance and refinement to wedding photos. Additionally, the palace garden offers a romantic landscape, perfect for outdoor photo sessions.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/contact/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tAsk For A Price Quotation\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<figure><img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Sedinta-foto-de-nunta-1-ql8uqkr09fw93tc5wh07zbhjwithctebh5xyn2p2gg.jpg\\" alt=\\"Sedinta foto de nunta\\" /></figure><figure><img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Nunta-de-vis-la-Palatul-Noblesse-4-ql8usqrm0ov1vg6u8wq989st7i4y3p01fw39h1he40.jpg\\" alt=\\"Nunta de vis la Palatul Noblesse\\" /></figure><figure><img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Sedinta-foto-de-nunta-Palatul-Noblesse-ql8uuws7rxtun31ilcgah842ihgeuklrem8kb09prk.jpg\\" alt=\\"Sedinta foto de nunta - Palatul Noblesse\\" /></figure>\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<figure><img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Sedinta-foto-la-Palatul-Noblesse-1-qlfi4slg3zl46cw8k8svt1i7bapwrk4ipdswg2dmsw.jpg\\" alt=\\"Sedinta foto la Palatul Noblesse\\" /></figure><figure><img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/SedintaFoto-194-qlfi4wcsvbq9gsqryafe30k1ou7dmcjg1weud681w8.jpg\\" alt=\\"SedintaFoto-194\\" /></figure><figure><img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Sedinta-foto-la-Palatul-Noblesse-2-qlfi5f5ko0fzwzzgwijxgvt9kjmpwam2shgjypg6nk.jpg\\" alt=\\"Sedinta foto la Palatul Noblesse\\" /></figure>\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Family Photo Sessions</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Family photos taken at Noblesse Palace acquire a special aura, in a historic and imposing setting. The moment spent with loved ones, in a fairytale location, will be immortalized in images that will always bring smiles and precious memories.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/contact/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tAsk For A Price Quotation\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h4>Why choose Noblesse palace</h4>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h4>Noblesse Palace - Historical Building</h4>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is the only fully consolidated and restored palace to the highest standards in Bucharest.</p><p>It is a historic building from the 19th century, the first eclectic-style building constructed in the center of Bucharest, bearing the signature of the famous architect Alexandru Săvulescu.</p><p>Noblesse Palace is a centrally located premium venue (situated in the center of Bucharest, just 5 minutes away from University Square).</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"800\\" height=\\"534\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-1024x683.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6.jpg 2048w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"800\\" height=\\"534\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7-1024x683.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7-768x512.jpg 768w, 