n%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTEzMjcsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wM1wvTG9yZWRhbmEtUHJlZGEtUGFsYXR1bC1Ob2JsZXNzZS5qcGVnIiwic2xpZGVzaG93IjoiNDc2Y2U1MTUifQ%3D%3D\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/events/category/private-events/photo-sessions/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tPhoto Sessions Portfolio\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h5>pLANNING A PHOTO SESSION?</h5>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Please fill out the contact form, and we will get back to you shortly with a personalized price quotation.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/contact/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tCONTACT FORM\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>", "meta_desc": "Noblesse Palace - Lifestyle Palace - the fairytale setting for professional photo sessions.", "date": "2024-04-15 09:02:16"},{"id": 12008, "title": "Biblioteka", "slug": "biblioteka", "parent_id": 0, "parent_slug": null, "type": "page", "content": "<h2>Biblioteka Hub is a space for inspiration and documentation, dedicated to courses, conferences, workshops, training sessions, brainstorming meetings, and last but not least, private events</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\tBiblioteka Hub represents an urban concept with industrial design created by <a href=\\"https://noblesse-group.com/\\">Noblesse Projects</a>, preserving the original brickwork of the 1881 building, brought to the highest standards through consolidation works, restoration, technical installations for underfloor heating, fresh air supply, and air conditioning. A detail that adds originality to the space is the glass ceiling above the room, supported by a very resistant metal structure.<br>Biblioteka Hub consists of two rooms, a main room and a secondary room serving as a space for coffee breaks and socializing. The logistical support provided is of the highest quality, with the room equipped with a video projector, laptop, fan coil units with thermostats for both cold and warm air, WI-FI internet, and a high-performance sound system. Biblioteka Hub has two entrances, one from the interior and one from the exterior, the latter leading directly to the terrace of Noblesse Palace - Lifestyle Palace, a spacious and relaxing area, an oasis of greenery and intimacy in the historic atmosphere of Bucharest.<br>All products used in the design of the Biblioteka Hub, such as furniture, lighting fixtures, flooring, accessories, and tiles, come from some of the largest and most renowned manufacturers of interior design objects, which are part of the <a href=\\"https://www.noblesseinteriors.com/\\">Noblesse Interiors</a> portfolio.\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/R-18-of-21.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"2831ad5a\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"R (18 of 21)\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTEzNTYsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wM1wvUi0xOC1vZi0yMS5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiIyODMxYWQ1YSJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Biiblioteka-Palatul-Noblesse.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"2831ad5a\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Foto: Alberto Groșescu\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTE2MDAsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wNFwvQmlpYmxpb3Rla2EtUGFsYXR1bC1Ob2JsZXNzZS5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiIyODMxYWQ1YSJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/R-14-of-21-light.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-eleme