                           read more                                </a>", "meta_desc": "Noblesse Palace - Ground-Floor - From the first steps inside Noblesse Palace, a world of classic elegance and refined luxury unfolds.", "date": "2024-04-14 08:13:17"},{"id": 12012, "title": "The Garden", "slug": "the-garden", "parent_id": 0, "parent_slug": null, "type": "page", "content": "<h2>With an area of 600 square meters, the Garden of Noblesse Palace is an oasis of peace and greenery, where you can successfully organize corporate events and private gatherings</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\tNoblesse Palace is surrounded by a landscaped space designed both for recreation and to enhance the entire ensemble. Of course, the structure of the original pathways that surrounded the house has been preserved, as well as the semi-circular driveway in front of the house, providing an entrance and exit for carriages or later automobiles, as there was no space for turning around. They entered from the direction of the street, stopped at the awning to pick up the owner, and exited through the second entrance facing the street.<br>Today, the Garden of Noblesse Palace is an oasis of peace and greenery amidst the urban hustle and bustle. It is a bohemian garden, in a Parisian style, with wide, paved pathways, enveloped in colors and light. Beneath tall trees, the walls are covered in ivy and illuminated by delicate lamps, while the pathways are bordered by bushes of red roses and white and pink hydrangeas. The curtain of lights along the central pathway creates a joyful atmosphere.\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Evenimente-corporate-in-aer-liber.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"768282dd\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Evenimente-corporate-in-aer-liber\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6ODgxOCwidXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6XC9cL3d3dy5wYWxhdHVsbm9ibG