htbox-slideshow=\\"768282dd\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Noble Drinks la Platul Noblesse\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6ODIzMywidXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6XC9cL3d3dy5wYWxhdHVsbm9ibGVzc2Uucm9cL3dwLWNvbnRlbnRcL3VwbG9hZHNcLzIwMjJcLzEwXC9BN18wMTczNi5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiI3NjgyODJkZCJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/A7_01732.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"768282dd\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Noble Drinks\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6NzM2MywidXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6XC9cL3d3dy5wYWxhdHVsbm9ibGVzc2Uucm9cL3dwLWNvbnRlbnRcL3VwbG9hZHNcLzIwMjJcLzA4XC9BN18wMTczMi5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiI3NjgyODJkZCJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\tThe Garden of Noblesse Palace can host private events such as weddings, receptions, christening, anniversary, or photo shoots, as well as corporate events such as gala dinners, conferences, networking events, product launches, and more.<br>When it comes to event planning in Bucharest, Noblesse Palace offers not only a versatile setting but also a full range of services including: a dedicated event manager, event design, personalized menus, floral arrangements, photo-video services, entertainment, guided tours of the palace, piano rental from 1800, refurbished and in perfect condition, and much more.", "meta_desc": "With an area of 600 square meters, the Garden of Noblesse Palace is an oasis of peace and greenery ...", "date": "2024-04-14 08:15:24"},{"id": 12014, "title": "Discover the Palace", "slug": "discover-the-palace", "parent_id": 0, "parent_slug": null, "type": "page", "content": "<h2>Palatul Noblesse – Lifestyle Palace<br>The Palace located in the Heart of Bucharest</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is an architectural gem that shines in the urban landscape of Bucharest, embodying classical elegance, grandeur, and a story that has been told for over 140 years. Located in the heart of the city, this historic building is a living representation of what can be achieved when two people have the will and passion for beauty. <a href=\\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/loredana-preda/\\">Loredana</a> and <a href=\\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/preda-silviu-4a45b9ab/\\">Silviu Preda</a> believed in their dream, and through hard work and dedication, they restored this beautiful building to its rightful place in Bucharest's architectural and cultural heritage.<br />Noblesse Palace has been transformed into an events and art center, successfully hosting dozens of private events, corporate gatherings, art exhibitions, fashion shows, product launches, and much more.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/ground-floor/\\"></a>\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h2 data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tDiscover<br>Noblesse palace\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h2>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tGround Floor\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"1365\\" height=\\"2048\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Paltul-Noblesse-08.jpg\\" alt=\\"Sala Baroque Palatul Noblesse\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Paltul-Noblesse-08.jpg 1365w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Paltul-Noblesse-08-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Paltul-Noblesse-08-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Paltul-Noblesse-08-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Paltul-Noblesse-08-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 1365px) 100vw, 1365px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatuln