oads/2024/04/Descopera-Palatul.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Descopera-Palatul.jpg 1365w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Descopera-Palatul-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Descopera-Palatul-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Descopera-Palatul-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Descopera-Palatul-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 1365px) 100vw, 1365px\\" />", "meta_desc": "Discover the Palace - Noblesse Palace is an architectural gem that shines in the urban landscape of Bucharest, embodying classical elegance...", "date": "2024-04-14 08:20:55"},{"id": 12019, "title": "Events Portfolio", "slug": "events-portfolio", "parent_id": 0, "parent_slug": null, "type": "page", "content": "<p>Special Moments That Live Forever!</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>EVENTS PORTFOLIO<br>FAIRYTALE EVENTS AT NOBLESSE PALACE</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>A 19th-century architectural gem, Noblesse Palace has been a witness and host to hundreds of private and corporate events over the years. With a rich history and unique charm, this historic building stands as the perfect choice for those seeking a premium venue for their special events.<br />The portfolio of events held at Noblesse Palace is vast and diverse, encompassing a wide range of special occasions. From weddings and christening to engagement parties and anniversaries, Noblesse Palace has witnessed many memorable moments in people's lives. Additionally, Noblesse Palace has hosted numerous corporate events, including conferences, Christmas parties, award ceremonies, product launches, workshops, team building events, and much more. Regardless of the nature of the event, our team of event organizers is prepared to transform every occasion into an unforgettable experience.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>private events portofolio</h2>\\t\\t\\n