dGEtZGUtdmlzLWxhLVBhbGF0dWwtTm9ibGVzc2UtMi0yLmpwZyIsInNsaWRlc2hvdyI6IjcxMmNhMTM3In0%3D\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/events/category/private-events/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tPrivate Events Portfolio\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h5>Planning a Private Event?</h5>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Please fill out the contact form, and we will get back to you shortly with a personalized price quotation.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/contact/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tContact Form\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>", "meta_desc": "From its opening until the present day, Noblesse Palace has hosted numerous private events (weddings, engagement parties, christening...", "date": "2024-04-15 07:52:43"},{"id": 12078, "title": "Private Parties", "slug": "private-parties", "parent_id": 0, "parent_slug": null, "type": "page", "content": "<p>Special Moments That Live Forever!</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>Noblesse Palace - Lifestyle Palace <br>The palace located in the heart of Bucharest</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\tNoblesse Palace, an architectural gem in the heart of the city, a location seemingly taken from storybooks, a setting filled with history and refinement, offers the perfect atmosphere to celebrate special moments in everyone's life, from an anniversary to a simple family reunion or a spectacular birthday party.<br>With its spectacular halls, each with a unique architectural design, Noblesse Palace is the ideal place to host private parties in an intimate and exclusive setting. Every detail in this historic palace exudes elegance and beauty, transforming events into true experiences.<br>Through its large windows, natural light floods the rooms, enhancing the warmth and joy of the party. The precious furniture, marble flooring, and contemporary artworks add a touch of refinement, harmoniously complementing the atmosphere of the event.\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/0052_Majorat_2022-q25d3dkgffuwnmjeqaqqx05qs18c8ebb91jvj1601k.jpg\\" title=\\"0052_Majorat_2022\\" alt=\\"0052_Majorat_2022\\" loading=\\"lazy\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"2048\\" height=\\"1362\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/0203_Majorat_2022.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/0203_Majorat_2022.jpg 2048w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/0203_Majorat_2022-600x399.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/0203_Majorat_2022-1024x681.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/0203_Majorat_2022-768x511.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/0203_Majorat_2022-1536x1022.jpg 1536w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"2048\\" height=\\"1362\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/0233_Majorat_2022.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/0233_Majorat_2022.jpg 2048w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/0233_Majorat_2022-600x399.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/0233_Majorat_2022-1024x681.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/0233_Majorat_2022-768x511.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/0233_Majorat_2022-1536x1022.jpg 1536w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>18th Birthday Party</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>In every young person's life, turning 18th years old represents an important moment, a milestone marking the transition from adolescence to adulthood. It's an event worthy of celebration in a fitting setting, one that offers the celebrant and guests a memorable experience.</p><p>Choosing the venue for a birthday celebration has a significant impact on the entire experience. Noblesse Palace, elegant and refined, provides an exceptional setting to mark this special occasion. Located in the heart of Bucharest, Noblesse Palace, this work of art, is the most suitable choice to commemorate the coming of age.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/contact/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tAsk For A Price Quotation\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<figure><img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Petrecere-majorat-la-Palatul-Noblesse-qm48erbuw1jgofumlvakv4qvz3mepwb5b0bm18isww.jpg\\" alt=\\"Petrecere majorat la Palatul Noblesse\\" /></figure><figure><img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Petreceri-de-Majorat-la-Palatul-Noblesse-qm48et7j9pm1bnrwaw3u049t5vd55ailz9mkzsg0kg.jpg\\" alt=\\"Petreceri de Majorat la Palatul Noblesse\\" /></figure><figure><img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Palatul-Noblesse-Petreceri-de-Majorat-qm48f6d9xe41u78s61slz0y9h9ka51yup2rdpnwi5c.jpg\\" alt=\\"Palatul Noblesse - Petreceri de Majorat\\" /></figure>\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<figure><img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Petreceri-private-la-Palatul-Noblesse-1-qm48fgpi0ki7dwtrho9i8gcc0i5bhq3wehxpzph68w.jpeg\\" alt=\\"Petreceri private la Palatul Noblesse\\" /></figure><figure><img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Palatul-Noblesse-Petreceri-Private-qm48fvqx1x2sjo7x1urjccjpio36wvrlskdho4uvhc.jpeg\\" alt=\\"Palatul Noblesse Petreceri Private\\" /></figure><figure><img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Palatul-Noblesse-Petrecere-Tematica-qlx5bfwga69rpf4qqbveiicztz0wpz6c1t2ukkpvc0.jpeg\\" alt=\\"Palatul Noblesse Petrecere Tematica\\" /></figure>\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>Anniversary Parties</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Planning and organizing an anniversary party is the perfect opportunity to transform a special event into a memorable one. Whether it's a birthday or a wedding anniversary, we invite you to discover Noblesse Palace, the palace in the heart of the city.</p><p>Turn this event into a memorable experience for both you and all your guests. Surround yourself with luxury and refinement and share this fairytale setting with your loved ones.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/contact/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tAsk For A Price Quotation\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Noblesse Palace Is A Historic Building</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is the only fully consolidated and restored palace to the highest standards in Bucharest.</p><p>It is a historic building from the 19th century, the first eclectic-style building constructed in the center of Bucharest, bearing the signature of the famous architect Alexandru Săvulescu.</p><p>Noblesse Palace is a centrally located premium venue (situated in the center of Bucharest, just 5 minutes away from University Square).</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"800\\" height=\\"534\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-1024x683.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-6.jpg 2048w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"800\\" height=\\"534\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7-1024x683.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-7.jpg 2048w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Noblesse Palace – Ballrooms</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Refinement and luxury are criteria found in all components of the palace, thanks to the team of architects from <a href=\\"https://noblesse-group.com/\\">Noblesse Group</a>.</p><p>The halls of Noblesse Palace are versatile, designed in various styles, ensuring intimacy and the possibility of organizing unique private parties.</p><p>Surrounded by a generous courtyard of 600 square meters, the palace is an oasis of greenery and privacy in the historic atmosphere of Bucharest.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Personalized Services</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Our event planners has the experience of hundreds of events organized, hundreds of memorable events, and thousands of memories created for every couple who has crossed our threshold.</p><p>Our team understands that each couple is unique and has their own desires and visions for their dream wedding. Therefore, the services offered are comprehensive and personalized to meet all the needs and desires of the newlyweds.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"800\\" height=\\"534\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-051-1024x683.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-051-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-051-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-051-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-051-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Nobless-shooting-051.jpg 2048w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h4>WHY CHOOSE NOBLESSE PALACE FOR YOUR PRIVATE PARTIES?</h4>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tDedicated event manager\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tEvent Design\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tPersonalized menus\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tFloral arrangements\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tPhoto & Video Services\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tEntertainment \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tPiano Rental from 1800\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h3>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h5>Planning A Private Party?</h5>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Please fill out the contact form, and we will get back to you shortly with a personalized price quotation.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/contact/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tContact Form\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>", "meta_desc": "With its spectacular halls, each with a unique architectural design, Noblesse Palace is the ideal place to host private parties in an intimate decor.", "date": "2024-04-15 08:42:10"},{"id": 12114, "title": "Our Concepts", "slug": "our-concepts", "parent_id": 11085, "parent_slug": "services", "type": "page", "content": "<p>Special Moments That Live Forever!</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>Our Concepts<br>Noblesse Palace – Lifestyle Palace<br>Art & Event Center</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\tNoblesse Palace is a historic building, a noble residence that tells its story for over 140 years. Brought back to life through extensive restoration and consolidation processes, which keep many of the original elements of the building alive, including the stuccoes, the two fireplaces, the joinery, and the exposed brick, Noblesse Palace is now an important center of culture, art, and design unique in Southwest Europe. It was created to bring people together in an oasis of eclectic style, dedicated to the most elegant and unique events.<br>And because we have created a dream universe where we have revived a long-lost world, bringing forth the charm and noble elegance of the 19th century, raising the bar to the highest standard, we have conceived, created, and organized some of the most appreciated events in art, culture, and socializing.<br>Through our concepts of events, we aim to immerse you in the emotionally charged atmosphere of the past palaces, where, for a few hours, we will convey you to a setting that will feel truly drawn from that era.\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Palatul-Noblesse-8-qlfibqmn6td2zpe0dowajyhvayehdr1agtstbnbwe0.jpg\\" title=\\"Botez Valeria\\" alt=\\"Botez Valeria\\" loading=\\"lazy\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"1920\\" height=\\"1280\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Noble-Drinks.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Noble-Drinks.jpg 1920w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Noble-Drinks-600x400.jpg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Noble-Drinks-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Noble-Drinks-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-Noble-Drinks-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"2048\\" height=\\"1365\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Expozitie-de-arta-Bucuresti.jpeg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Expozitie-de-arta-Bucuresti.jpeg 2048w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Expozitie-de-arta-Bucuresti-600x400.jpeg 600w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Expozitie-de-arta-Bucuresti-1024x683.jpeg 1024w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Expozitie-de-arta-Bucuresti-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Expozitie-de-arta-Bucuresti-1536x1024.jpeg 1536w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Fusion Arts<br>Art Event</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p><a href=\\"https://fusionarts.ro/\\">Fusion Arts</a> is a distinctive event concept developed and supported by <a href=\\"https://noblesse-group.com/\\">Noblesse Group</a> and Noblesse Palace.</p><p>The mission of Fusion Arts is to encourage appreciation, understanding, and the role of art in society through direct engagement with original artworks. The primary priority is to inspire artists, clients, and our local guests with amazing projects.</p><p>Through Fusion Arts, Noblesse Palace promotes urban culture, bringing artists from various fields closer to the public through diverse events, including exhibitions, vernissages, urban 