\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"7dd8fc13\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Sala Gallery Palatul Noblesse (2)\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTE1MTEsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wNFwvU2FsYS1HYWxsZXJ5LVBhbGF0dWwtTm9ibGVzc2UtMi5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiI3ZGQ4ZmMxMyJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Sala-Gallery-Palatul-Noblesse-1.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"7dd8fc13\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Sala Gallery Palatul Noblesse\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTE1MTIsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wNFwvU2FsYS1HYWxsZXJ5LVBhbGF0dWwtTm9ibGVzc2UtMS5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiI3ZGQ4ZmMxMyJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t<em>Stuccoes - original<br>Carpentry - original</em>\\n<em>Flooring - marble in a combination of white and black, a geometric pattern created using the \\"water-jet\\" technique<br>Artworks - contemporary artists, <a href=\\"https://fusionarts.ro/\\">Fusion Arts</a> portfolio<br>Furniture pieces - <a href=\\"https://www.noblesseinteriors.com/\\">Noblesse Interiors</a> portfolio<br>\\n<strong>When it comes to organizing events in Bucharest, Noblesse Palace offers, in addition to a versatile setting, a full range of services such as: dedicated event manager, event design, personalized menus, floral arrangements, photo-video services, entertainment, guided tour of the palace, piano rental from 1800, refurbished and in perfect condition, and many more.</strong>\\n<strong>Moreover, we organize a wide range of events, from art exhibitions and fairs to private and corporate events, as well as charitable events.</strong>", "meta_desc": "The Gallery Room is the first room on the left of the central hallway.", "date": "2024-04-15 13:14:23"},{"id": 12149, "title": "Luxury Hall", "slug": "luxury-hall", "parent_id": 12010, "parent_slug": "ground-floor", "type": "page", "content": "<h2>The Luxury Hall immerses us in an elegant atmosphere, with luxury notes highlighted by the eclectic style, natural light, and statement painting adorning one of the room's walls</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>The Luxury Hall is located to the right of the central hallway and, as the name suggests, is adorned with many luxury pieces, from furniture by famous brands to luxurious decorations. This room is truly a select chamber, a delight even for the most discerning observers. Yet the room bears the imprint of the old stuccoes restored, painted white to further highlight the beauty of the furniture and luxurious decorations. The floor is made of specially treated marble, in contrasting shades of black and white, just enough to complement each other in a simple yet luxurious play.<br />The Luxury Hall can be rented separately for private or business dinners, discussions, and business meetings, as well as for photo shoots or product presentations.<br />The room has an area of 25 square meters and can accommodate up to 14 people. It is equipped with a video projector, screen, flipchart, air conditioning, Wi-Fi.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Sala-Luxury-Palatul-Noblesse-1.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"5fe98893\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Sala Luxury - Palatul Noblesse\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTE1MjEsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wNFwvU2FsYS1MdXh1cnktUGFsYXR1bC1Ob2JsZXNzZS0xLmpwZyIsInNsaWRlc2hvdyI6IjVmZTk4ODkzIn0%3D\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<