xvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wNFwvU2FsYS1SZWdlbnQtMi5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiI1ZjdjMGYzYSJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t<p><em>Plasterwork – original</em><br /><em>Carpentry – original</em><br /><em>Flooring – marble in a combination of black and white, a geometric pattern created using the \\"water-jet\\" technique</em><br /><em>Artworks – contemporary artists, <a href=\\"https://fusionarts.ro/\\">Fusion Arts</a> portfolio</em><br /><em>Furniture pieces – <a href=\\"https://www.noblesseinteriors.com/\\">Noblesse Interiors</a> portfolio</em></p><p><strong>When it comes to organizing events in Bucharest, Palatul Noblesse offers, alongside a versatile setting, a complete range of services such as: dedicated event manager, event design, personalized menus, floral arrangements, photo-video services, entertainment, guided tours of the palace, rental of a piano from 1800, refurbished and in perfect condition, and much more. Additionally, we organize events of all kinds, from art exhibitions and fairs, to private and corporate events, as well as charitable events.</strong></p>", "meta_desc": "To the right of the Baroque Hall, a new room opens up, different from all the others, the Regent Hall", "date": "2024-04-15 14:06:15"},{"id": 12178, "title": "Opera Kitchen", "slug": "opera-kitchen", "parent_id": 12010, "parent_slug": "ground-floor", "type": "page", "content": "<h2>The Opera Kitchen is a favorite among gastronomy experts</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Because we understand how important food service is at special events, we've designed a spacious kitchen located in close proximity to the halls. The Opera Kitchen is furnished in the same elegant and classic style as all the rooms on the ground floor of the Noblesse Palace, making it perfect for preparing refined dishes and cooking shows.<br />It is equipped with a fully functional kitchen, with beige wooden cabinets, an exceptional granite countertop, a gas stove, and an oven crafted from a material that resembles copper. The floor is made of marble, in shades of white, beige, yellow, and brown, resembling a real carpet.</p><p>The room has an area of ​​20 square meters and can also be used as space for serving coffee breaks or setting up the bar.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bucataria-Opera-Palatul-Noblesse-1.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"3f73403b\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Bucataria Opera Palatul Noblesse\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTE1NTYsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wNFwvQnVjYXRhcmlhLU9wZXJhLVBhbGF0dWwtTm9ibGVzc2UtMS5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiIzZjczNDAzYiJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Bucataria-Opera-Palatul-Noblesse.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"3f73403b\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Bucataria Opera Palatul Noblesse\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTE1NTQsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wNFwvQnVjYXRhcmlhLU9wZXJhLVBhbGF0dWwtTm9ibGVzc2UuanBnIiwic2xpZGVzaG93IjoiM2Y3MzQwM2IifQ%3D%3D\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Palatul-Noblesse-08.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"3f73403b\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Palatul Noblesse 08\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTE1NTUsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wNFwvUGFsYXR1bC1Ob2JsZXNzZS0wOC5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiIzZjczNDAzYiJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>", "meta_desc": "he Opera Kitchen is furnished in the same elegant and classic style as all the rooms on the ground floor of the Noblesse Palace, making it perfect...", "date": "2024-04-15 14:13:52"},{"id": 12183, "title": "Regent Bathroom", "slug": "regent-bathroom", "parent_id": 12010, "parent_slug": "ground-floor", "type": "page", "content": "<h2>The elegant and sophisticated ambiance of Palatul Noblesse is complemented by the exquisite restroom located on the ground floor, adjacent to the Regent Hall</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>The Regent bathroom is designed in a classic manner with Victorian influences, highlighted by the unmistakable style of the flooring as well as the furniture elements. The basin, crafted from rare wood, adds a distinct elegance to the room, perfectly complemented by the mirror adorned with gold leaf. An impressive bathtub is among the spectacular features of this bathroom. The copper-footed tub sits in front of the window, enveloped in a delicate curtain and burgundy velvet drapes.<br />Special wallpaper and marble flooring, both in shades of white and burgundy, grace this bathroom. The walls of this bathroom are adorned with impressive paintings, signed by Romanian artists featured in the <a href=\\"https://fusionarts.ro/\\">Fusion Arts</a> portfolio.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Baia-Regent.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"30f1ce29\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Baia Regent\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTE1NjEsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wNFwvQmFpYS1SZWdlbnQuanBnIiwic2xpZGVzaG93IjoiMzBmMWNlMjkifQ%3D%3D\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Baia-Regent-1.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"30f1ce29\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Baia Regent\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTE1NjMsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wNFwvQmFpYS1SZWdlbnQtMS5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiIzMGYxY2UyOSJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Baia-Regent-2.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"30f1ce29\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Baia Regent (2)\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTE1NjIsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wNFwvQmFpYS1SZWdlbnQtMi5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiIzMGYxY2UyOSJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Baia-Regent-2-1.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"30f1ce29\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Baia Regent (2)\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTE1NjQsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wNFwvQmFpYS1SZWdlbnQtMi0xLmpwZyIsInNsaWRlc2hvdyI6IjMwZjFjZTI5In0%3D\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Baia-Regent-3.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"30f1ce29\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Baia Regent (3)\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTE1NjUsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wNFwvQmFpYS1SZWdlbnQtMy5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiIzMGYxY2UyOSJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Baia-Regent-4.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"30f1ce29\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Baia Regent (4)\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTE1NjYsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wNFwvQmFpYS1SZWdlbnQtNC5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiIzMGYxY2UyOSJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>", "meta_desc": "The Regent bathroom is designed in a classic manner with Victorian influences, highlighted by the unmistakable style of the flooring as well...", "date": "2024-04-15 14:18:38"},{"id": 12188, "title": "Luxury Bathroom", "slug": "luxury-bathroom", "parent_id": 12010, "parent_slug": "ground-floor", "type": "page", "content": "<h2>Exploring the ground floor of Palatul Noblesse, near the central staircase, you will encounter a relatively small room, the Luxury Bathroom, which will impress you with its unique beauty as soon as you cross its threshold</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>The beauty of this palace will certainly be found in the Luxury Bathroom as well. Located on the ground floor of the palace, the Luxury Bathroom expresses its personality through both the refined patterned ceramics and the delicately crafted mosaic with gold leaf, bearing the signature of a famous brand, both in the interior design industry and in fashion. The bathroom's statement piece is the impressive crystal chandelier, followed by the classic mirror, the gold-plated accessories and faucet, adorned with crystals.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Baia-Luxury-2.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"1f244489\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Baia Luxury (2)\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTE1NzIsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wNFwvQmFpYS1MdXh1cnktMi5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiIxZjI0NDQ4OSJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Baia-Luxury.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"1f244489\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Baia Luxury\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTE1NzEsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wNFwvQmFpYS1MdXh1cnkuanBnIiwic2xpZGVzaG93IjoiMWYyNDQ0ODkifQ%3D%3D\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Baia-Luxury-3.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"1f244489\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Baia Luxury (3)\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTE1NzMsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wNFwvQmFpYS1MdXh1cnktMy5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiIxZjI0NDQ4OSJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>", "meta_desc": "The beauty of this palace will certainly be found in the Luxury Bathroom as well. Located on the ground floor of the palace...", "date": "2024-04-15 14:23:57"},{"id": 12197, "title": "About Us", "slug": "about-us", "parent_id": 0, "parent_slug": null, "type": "page", "content": "<p>Discover The Palace Located In The Heart Of Bucharest</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h2>NOBLESSE PALACE<br>ABOUT US</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>The Noblesse Palace was the residence of the Berkovitz family, a Jewish family well anchored in the financial system of old Romania, which survived economic crises, wars, and various occupations, but disappeared almost a hundred years after its story began, with the nationalization in the early 1950s.<br />The building was erected at the end of the 19th century in an old neighborhood of Bucharest in the central sector of Roșu, at the intersection of Sfinților Street with Calea Moșilor, across from the church of the Saints or \\"with Sibile.\\" It was restored to the city in all its splendor by <a href=\\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/loredana-preda/\\">Loredana</a> and <a href=\\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/preda-silviu-4a45b9ab/\\">Silviu Preda</a>. Its story is of course linked to the place where it was built, then the city and the neighborhood, to the people who lived on this street, to the neighborhoods that prompted the Berkowitz family to buy and live here for at least two generations.</p><p>We invite you to discover our story, in a short history lesson about people, places, and events.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h2 data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tNOBLESSE palace\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h2>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tOverview\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"1365\\" height=\\"2048\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CN-92-of-96.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CN-92-of-96.jpg 1365w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CN-92-of-96-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CN-92-of-96-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CN-92-of-96-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/CN-92-of-96-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 1365px) 100vw, 1365px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>The Noblesse Palace is a space dedicated to classic elegance, imposing and fascinating through every architectural detail found within its halls.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/overview/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tDISCOVER MORE\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h2 data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tNoblesse Palace\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h2>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tThe Story Of The Palace\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"1365\\" height=\\"2048\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/foto-126.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/foto-126.jpg 1365w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/foto-126-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/foto-126-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/foto-126-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/foto-126-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 1365px) 100vw, 1365px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>The first eclectic building in Bucharest, Palatul Noblesse is a historic monument builted in 1881 according to the plans of the architect Alexandru Săvulescu.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/the-story-of-the-palace/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tDISCOVER MORE\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h2 data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tNoblesse Palace\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h2>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tHistorical research\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"1365\\" height=\\"2048\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Istoria-Palatului-Noblesse-Planuri-Alexandru-Savulescu-4-1.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Istoria-Palatului-Noblesse-Planuri-Alexandru-Savulescu-4-1.jpg 1365w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Istoria-Palatului-Noblesse-Planuri-Alexandru-Savulescu-4-1-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Istoria-Palatului-Noblesse-Planuri-Alexandru-Savulescu-4-1-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Istoria-Palatului-Noblesse-Planuri-Alexandru-Savulescu-4-1-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Istoria-Palatului-Noblesse-Planuri-Alexandru-Savulescu-4-1-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 1365px) 100vw, 1365px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>The history of Palatul Noblesse is closely tied to the place where this  building was constructed, the city, the neighborhood, and the people who lived in it.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/en/historical-research/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tDISCOVER MORE\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<h2 data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tNoblesse Palace\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</h2>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p data-settings=\\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;&quot;}\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tRestoration\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<img width=\\"1365\\" height=\\"2048\\" src=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_5194.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" srcset=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_5194.jpg 1365w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_5194-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_5194-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_5194-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_5194-1024x1536.jpg 1024w\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 1365px) 100vw, 1365px\\" />\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>The former Berkowitz residence now has a new appearance, full of splendor, thanks to the meticulous restoration efforts carried out by the <a href=\\"https://noblesse-group.com/\\">Noblesse Group</a> team.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/restaurare/%20\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tDISCOVER MORE\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Why Choose Noblesse Palace?</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tSix rooms with different styles, comprising the ground floor of Noblesse Palace (Gallery, Luxury, Regent, Florence, Baroque and Opera)\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tBiblioteka is a unique space located in the basement with direct access to the garden. Here you can organize small  events\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tThe bohemian garden, a generous courtyard of 600 square meters, an oasis of greenery and intimacy in the historic atmosphere of Bucharest\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tMaximum capacity indoors is 100 people (seated) and 300 people (cocktail style)\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tNearby parking spaces, available upon request\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tThe Noblesse Palace is equipped with state-of-the-art technological facilities\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</p>\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>19th century historical building</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is a historical building from the 19th century, is the first building with an eclectic architecture built in this old area of Bucharest, and bears the signature of the famous romanian architect Alexandru Săvulescu.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Fully consolidated and restored building</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is the only completely consolidated and restored palace to the highest standards in Bucharest, where luxurious architecture merges with its intimate elegance.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Central Premium Venue</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace is a premium venue located in the center of Bucharest, near Universitate Square, just 5 minutes away from Universitate metro station.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>unique experience</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Noblesse Palace offers a unique and comprehensive experience. Rediscover 135 years of history brought to life by the architects and designers of Noblesse Group.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Exclusive tours of the palace</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>You can enjoy exclusive tours of Noblesse Palace. During this tours you can have the opportunity to visit Fusion Arts exhibitions, as well as the latest international interior design collections in the Noblesse Group portfolio.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>We have experience in organizing hundreds of events</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>With experience in hundreds of successful events organized for major companies across all industries, as well as private clients, Noblesse Palace has hosted weddings, baptisms, birthdays parties, conferences, workshops, product launches, and much more.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>THE CHURCH OF THE SAINTS ACROSS THE ROAD</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>The Church of the Saints in Bucharest is located next to the Noblesse Palace. This small church is famous for the sibyls on its walls, which have been preserved so well over time. Welcoming and warm, it has witnessed many beautiful stories organized at Noblesse Palace, with many brides and grooms and parents choosing this church for religious ceremonies.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>MASTER BEDROOM AVAILABLE DURING THE EVENT</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>For rest and comfort of the bride and groom or the parents, Noblesse Palace offers an apartment on the upper floor, the Princess Room, fully functional and equipped to the highest standards, ensuring that the evening spent at the Palace will be truly memorable.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h3>Noblesse Palace <br/>\\nEvent & Art Center In bucharest</h3>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>Step into the Universe of Palatul Noblesse and explore each room, discovering a location full of history and stories.</p><p>As an events and art center, Palatul Noblesse stands as a true architectural and cultural gem in the heart of Bucharest.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"/turvirtual/\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tVirtual Tour\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>", "meta_desc": "About Us - The Noblesse Palace was the residence of the Berkovitz family, a Jewish family well anchored in the financial system of old Romania", "date": "2024-04-15 15:50:57"},{"id": 12199, "title": "Overview", "slug": "overview", "parent_id": 0, "parent_slug": null, "type": "page", "content": "<h2>Noblesse Palace – Lifestyle Palace<br>Overview</h2>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<p>The Noblesse Palace is a space dedicated to classic elegance, imposing and fascinating through every architectural detail found within its halls. It is a premium central venue for private events, corporate events, art events, networking events, and more.<br />The Noblesse Palace is a historic building, an architectural jewel from the 19th century, located in the heart of the city, representing a symbol of refinement and prestige. Designed by the renowned Romanian architect Alexandru Săvulescu, who also built the National History Museum of Romania, the Noblesse Palace is among the first buildings constructed in eclectic style in Bucharest, symbolizing the refinement of the city.<br />Despite being a historic building, the Noblesse Palace boasts modern state-of-the-art facilities, ensuring the comfort and satisfaction of its guests. From high-quality audio-visual equipment to climate control systems and other premium amenities, everything is provided to ensure a flawless event. The dedicated team at the Noblesse Palace offers personalized services and special attention to the needs of each guest, guaranteeing a successful and unforgettable event.<br />Today, the Noblesse Palace successfully hosts corporate and private events, while also serving as the headquarters of the <a href=\\"https://noblesse-group.com/\\">Noblesse Projects</a> architecture firm, an exclusive showroom for the collections in the <a href=\\"https://www.noblesseinteriors.com/\\">Noblesse Interiors</a> portfolio, and an art gallery showcasing both its own collection of paintings and sculptures, as well as temporary exhibitions by contemporary artists.</p>\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-9.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"49f7e97a\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Palatul Noblesse\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTEwMDQsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wM1wvUGFsYXR1bC1Ob2JsZXNzZS05LmpwZyIsInNsaWRlc2hvdyI6IjQ5ZjdlOTdhIn0%3D\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Palatul-Noblesse-03-1.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"49f7e97a\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Palatul Noblesse 03\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTEwMDgsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wM1wvUGFsYXR1bC1Ob2JsZXNzZS0wMy0xLmpwZyIsInNsaWRlc2hvdyI6IjQ5ZjdlOTdhIn0%3D\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t</a>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<a href=\\"https://www.palatulnoblesse.ro/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Tavanul.jpg\\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\\"yes\\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\\"49f7e97a\\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\\"Tavanul\\" data-e-action-hash=\\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6MTEwMjQsInVybCI6Imh0dHBzOlwvXC93d3cucGFsYXR1bG5vYmxlc3NlLnJvXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8wM1wvVGF2YW51bC5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiI0OWY3ZTk3YSJ9\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\